            <scopecontent id="aspace_1d7a273fc61af0c7a860122af73c196c">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The Edward Clark Streeter Papers are composed of letters addressed to Edward Clark Streeter, primarily by Fielding H. Garrison. The Garrison letters, which date from 1914-1932, are arranged in chronological order at the beginning of the papers. They are followed by one folder of letters received from others. The Medical Historical Library transferred the papers to Manuscripts and Archives in 1994.</p>
            </scopecontent>
